<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Home - Accela</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/chapters.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="https://files.catbox.moe/bpi1je.gif" type="image/gif">
  <script>
    (function() {
      var t = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'dark';
      document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', t);
    })();
  </script>
  <style>
    .user-status {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      right: 40px;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      background: var(--bg-btn);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .user-status.premium { background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3); color: #ffd700; }
    .user-status.admin { background: rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.4); color: #da70d6; }

    .days-left { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.85; margin-top: 4px; }
    .days-left.warning { color: #ff6b6b; }
    .days-left.good { color: #4ade80; }
    .upgrade-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: #00ffcc; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
    .upgrade-link:hover { opacity: 0.8; text-decoration: underline; }

    .header-login-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      right: 40px;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      background: rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.4);
      color: #00ffcc;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .header-login-btn:hover { background: #00ffcc; color: #000; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.4); }

    .home-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .home-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px 32px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: block;
    }
    .home-card:hover { background: var(--bg-card-hover); transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover); }
    .home-card-icon { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; }
    .home-card h2 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text); }
    .home-card p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

    .pitch-headline { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #00ffcc); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    [data-theme="light"] .pitch-headline { background: linear-gradient(to right, #1a1833, #00b890); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    .pitch-subhead { font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 25px; font-style: italic; }
    .feature-list { text-align: left; margin: 20px auto; max-width: 600px; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .feature-list li { margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); }

    .pricing-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.1), rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1));
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    [data-theme="light"] .pricing-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 184, 144, 0.08), rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.08)); }
    .price-tag { font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #00ffcc; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    [data-theme="light"] .price-tag { color: #00996e; }

    .big-cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #00ffcc; color: #000; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.3); transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
    .big-cta-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.6); }

    .contact-section { background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-top: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .contact-section h3 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--text); }
    .contact-links { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 16px; }
    .contact-btn { background: var(--bg-btn); color: var(--text); padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-btn); font-size: 15px; }
    .contact-btn:hover { background: var(--bg-btn-hover); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .highlight { color: #00ffcc; font-weight: 600; }
    [data-theme="light"] .highlight { color: #00996e; }
    .warning-box { background: rgba(255, 59, 48, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 59, 48, 0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 20px; color: #ff6b6b; font-size: 15px; }

    .premium-banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.15), rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.15)); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 24px; margin: 20px auto; max-width: 900px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
    .premium-banner.expiring-soon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.15), rgba(255, 50, 50, 0.15)); border-color: rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.4); }
    .premium-banner-text { color: var(--text); font-size: 15px; }
    .premium-banner-text strong { color: #ffd700; }
    .premium-banner.expiring-soon .premium-banner-text strong { color: #ff6b6b; }
    .renew-btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #ff8c00); color: #000; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
    .renew-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4); }

    .text { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; text-align: left; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .user-status, .header-login-btn { position: static; transform: none; margin: 16px auto; text-align: center; max-width: 200px; display: block; }
      .home-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
      .home-card { padding: 32px 24px; }
      .home-card-icon { font-size: 48px; }
      .pitch-headline { font-size: 24px; }
      .contact-links { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .contact-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
      .premium-banner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="header" style="position: relative;">
    <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" onclick="toggleTheme()" title="Toggle theme">☀️</button>
    <div class="logo-title">
      <img src="https://files.catbox.moe/bpi1je.gif" alt="Animated Accela Logo" class="logo" />
      <h1 id="accela">Accela</h1>
    </div>

    <% if (isAuthenticated && user) { %>
      <div class="user-status <%= isAdmin ? 'admin' : (hasPremium ? 'premium' : '') %>">
        <% if (isAdmin) { %>
          👑 Admin
        <% } else if (hasPremium) { %>
          ⭐ Premium User
          <% if (daysLeft !== Infinity && daysLeft > 0) { %>
            <div class="days-left <%= daysLeft <= 7 ? 'warning' : 'good' %>">
              <% if (daysLeft <= 7) { %>⚠ <%= daysLeft %> day<%= daysLeft !== 1 ? 's' : '' %> left
              <% } else { %><%= daysLeft %> days remaining<% } %>
            </div>
          <% } else if (daysLeft === Infinity) { %>
            <div class="days-left good">Lifetime Access</div>
          <% } %>
        <% } else { %>
          👤 <%= user.username %>
          <a href="/upgrade?username=<%= user.username %>" class="upgrade-link">⬆ Upgrade to Premium</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/login" class="header-login-btn">Login / Sign Up</a>
    <% } %>
  </header>

  <% if (isAuthenticated && hasPremium && !isAdmin && daysLeft <= 7 && daysLeft > 0 && daysLeft !== Infinity) { %>
    <div class="premium-banner expiring-soon" style="margin-left:20px; margin-right:20px;">
      <div class="premium-banner-text">
        ⚠ Your premium expires in <strong><%= daysLeft %> day<%= daysLeft !== 1 ? 's' : '' %></strong>. Renew now!
      </div>
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="home-grid">
    <a href="/notes" class="home-card">
      <span class="home-card-icon">📝</span>
      <h2>Smart Notes</h2>
      <p>Boring Textbooks ka nichod. Seedha dimaag mein utarne wali easy Urdu.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/chapters" class="home-card">
      <span class="home-card-icon">📂</span>
      <h2>Flashcards</h2>
      <p>Ratta maarna band. Sawalon ke jawab do aur memory permanent karo.</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <section id="lain" class="section lain-section">
    <div class="lain-container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2 class="pitch-headline">Syllabus Yaad Nahi Hota?<br>Ratta Maarna Band Karo.</h2>
      <p class="pitch-subhead">ACCELA: The Only System Designed for BUMS Students — 4 Pharmacy Subjects, Ek Jagah.</p>

      <img src="https://files.catbox.moe/bpi1je.gif" alt="ACCELA Logo" class="lain-img" style="margin: 20px auto;" />

      <p class="text">
        <strong>Sach bolo, ye scenario familiar hai?</strong><br>
        Exam sar par hai. Aapne moti kitaab kholi. Pehle 2 page padhe, aur neend aane lagi. Dawaiyon ke naam, unki khasiyat aur tarikeeb sab mix ho raha hai — dimaag mein "Khichdi" ban gayi hai.
        <br><br>
        Aap padh toh rahe ho, lekin <strong>yaad</strong> kuch nahi reh raha.
        <br><br>
        <span class="highlight">Problem aap nahi ho, problem aapka "Method" hai.</span><br>
        Sirf reading karne se cheezein yaad nahi hoti. Agar bina samjhe ratta maaroge, toh exam hall mein blank ho jaoge.
        <br><br>
        <strong>Enter ACCELA (The Cheat Code):</strong><br>
        Humne woh boring text ko tod kar <strong>Smart Notes</strong> aur <strong>Active Recall Flashcards</strong> mein convert kar diya hai — tamam 4 subjects ke liye.
      </p>

      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>✅ <strong>4 Subjects:</strong> Kulliyate Advia, Advia Mufradat, Ilmul Saidla, Advia Murakkabat — sab ek jagah.</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Time Saver:</strong> Jo chapter 3 ghante leta hai, wo yahan 30 min mein pakka.</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Urdu Notes:</strong> Simple zubaan, no complicated words.</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Exam Ready:</strong> Hum sirf syllabus nahi, exam pass karwate hain.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="pricing-box">
        <span class="price-tag">₹499</span>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0;">Per term — less than one pizza</p>
        <hr style="border-color: var(--border); margin: 15px 0;">
        <p style="color: var(--text); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;">
          📘 <strong style="color:#00ffcc;">Term 1 / Term 2 / Term 3:</strong> ₹499 each — all 4 subjects included<br>
          🏆 <strong style="color:#ffd700;">Complete Syllabus:</strong> ₹999 <span style="color:var(--text-muted);">(all 3 terms × 4 subjects)</span><br>
          ⏳ Every plan stays active for <strong>18 months</strong> from purchase.<br>
          📚 Includes notes <em>and</em> flashcards for the term you buy.
        </p>
        <% if (!isAuthenticated) { %>
          <br>
          <a href="/login" class="big-cta-btn">Start Studying Now (Login)</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <h3>📩 Kisi Madad Ki Zaroorat Hai?</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 12px;">Direct support for Students</p>
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="mailto:accela.official@gmail.com" class="contact-btn" onclick="window.open(this.href, '_system'); return false;">
            📧 Email Support
          </a>
          <a href="https://t.me/AccelaSupportbot" class="contact-btn" onclick="window.open(this.href, '_system'); return false;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            💬 Telegram
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="cbox" class="section">
    <h2>Dimaag mein koi sawal? (Ask here)</h2>
    <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
      Koi doubt hai? Specific topic chahiye? Niche likho, personally check karke jawab milega.
    </p>
    <iframe src="https://www5.cbox.ws/box/?boxid=957561&boxtag=IZAjsP"
      allow="autoplay" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" scrolling="auto"></iframe>
  </section>

  <section id="updates" class="section">
    <h2 id="siteupdate">What's New</h2>
    <ul class="updates">
      <li>🧪 <strong>4 Subjects added</strong> — Kulliyate Advia, Advia Mufradat, Ilmul Saidla, aur Advia Murakkabat sab ek platform par.</li>
      <li>🧩 <strong>Term-based plans</strong> — Buy Term 1, Term 2, or Term 3 (₹499 each) — covers all 4 subjects for that term. Or get Complete (₹999) for everything.</li>
      <li>⏳ <strong>18-month validity</strong> — Every plan stays active for 18 months from purchase. No mid-prep cut-off.</li>
      <li>☀️ <strong>Light / Dark theme</strong> — Sun icon (top-left of header) dabao, theme switch ho jaega.</li>
      <li>📧 <strong>Email verification & password reset</strong> — Forgot your password? Reset it yourself from the login page.</li>
      <li>👤 <strong>Profile page</strong> — See every plan you own and its individual expiry date in one place.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="warning-box">
      <strong>⚠ Important:</strong> Account sharing allow nahi hai. Har account ek device se lock ho jaata hai. Agar multiple logo ne ek ID use ki, system auto-block kar dega bina refund ke. Play fair.
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="buttons-container">
    <div class="button-row">
      <% if (isAuthenticated) { %>
        <form action="/logout" method="GET"><button type="submit" class="logout-btn">Logout</button></form>
        <% if (user && user.role === 'admin') { %><a href="/admin" class="admin-btn">Admin Panel</a><% } %>
        <a href="/profile" class="admin-btn" style="background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3); border-color: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);">Profile</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login" class="admin-btn">Login / Sign Up</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleTheme() {
      var html = document.documentElement;
      var current = html.getAttribute('data-theme') || 'dark';
      var next = current === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
      html.setAttribute('data-theme', next);
      localStorage.setItem('theme', next);
      document.getElementById('themeToggle').textContent = next === 'dark' ? '☀️' : '🌙';
    }
    (function() {
      var t = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'dark';
      document.getElementById('themeToggle').textContent = t === 'dark' ? '☀️' : '🌙';
    })();
  </script>

</body>
</html>
